                "key": "Extinguishing Precept",
                "string_values": [
                  "<p>Gain <span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">12%/15%/18%/21%/24%</span> All Elemental DMG Bonus. Obtain Consummation for 20s after using an Elemental Skill, causing ATK to increase by <span style=\"color: rgb(55, 255, 255)\">3.2%/4%/4.8%/5.6%/6.4%</span> per second. This ATK increase has a maximum of 6 stacks. When the character equipped with this weapon is not on the field, Consummation's ATK increase is doubled.</p>"
